{"tid":2093618,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"莫迪親臨中印邊境「發炮」： 危害和平霸權必敗","createTime":"2020-07-04T03:33:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T04:50:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"673489578c05734b9b841ebcf81f4e1701813a37","tid":2093618,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:33:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200704/4OJQ36BVRVCKGKL3VO6SZU7HCE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200704%2F4OJQ36BVRVCKGKL3VO6SZU7HCE%2F&d=C%2Fe7%2FQel5OtnIpuNpUi2II%2FVxAEwmAwDimrVtn2syv4%3D&h=f0031d54\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200704%2F4OJQ36BVRVCKGKL3VO6SZU7HCE%2F&h=689bea0d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200704/4OJQ36BVRVCKGKL3VO6SZU7HCE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n莫迪親臨中印邊境「發炮」：<br />\n危害和平霸權必敗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中印自上月初邊境爆致命衝突後，兩國在民間、經濟，甚至在軍事調配上都互相敵視。印度總理莫迪昨早突然到訪印度邊境城市Nimu，並向駐軍稱：「敵人已看到你們的怒火。」他不點名警告中國：「霸權時代已結束，一些國家的擴張主義行為已危及世界和平。」印度國防部日前還緊急向俄羅斯提交了一份軍火採購清單，總值超過10億美元（約78億港元），大部份是坦克及裝甲武器。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/15080QnrF3BL7zZmeL6aXC7Wvb8=/1670x2024/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5DHBE4RJJ7GZO3JAYX3BWZRKCQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F15080QnrF3BL7zZmeL6aXC7Wvb8%3D%2F1670x2024%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5DHBE4RJJ7GZO3JAYX3BWZRKCQ.gif&h=374d8d2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫迪在軍頭陪同下現身邊境城市Nimu視察。<br />\n<br />\n莫迪昨早在沒有事先通知下，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n14軍的事迹亦已家喻戶曉。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n激昂發言鼓勵「怒火軍團」<br />\n<br />\n14軍素有「怒火軍團」（Fire And Fury Corps）之稱，莫迪更揚言：「印度的敵人相信已看到你們的怒火」。莫迪話鋒一轉，突然不點名批評中國的政策。他說：「現在是建設的時間，並不是擴張及霸權時間。某些國家的霸權，已經影響世界和平。歷史已證明這些主張霸權的國家，一是落敗，一是被迫撤退。」<br />\n<br />\n莫迪近日與中國關係頗為惡劣，<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n並同意在今年年底前在印度舉行雙邊年度會談。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/edIXmWcAYAPyDyt9vtwZfZ2QcGk=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/N6HATYLQS6ZMLOHXBLUVS7RSDE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FedIXmWcAYAPyDyt9vtwZfZ2QcGk%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FN6HATYLQS6ZMLOHXBLUVS7RSDE.jpg&h=b57d5dff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度向邊境增兵傳已近8萬。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n購俄軍火 普京允加強關係<br />\n<br />\n除了外交，印度亦加緊購買俄製軍備。<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n印度對最新式的T-14「阿爾瑪塔」主戰坦克感興趣，俄羅斯正在為這筆交易做準備。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部昨<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n印度短視頻程式Roposo表示，抖音被禁後的48小時內，程式下載數目增加了2,200萬次。<br />\n<br />\nBUSINESS TODAY/《印度時報》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vIxsoZef9DrY2zKbfvRPqzz5qes=/501x337/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RPXVLDNMPQAAPGNMYYODOVKW2A.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvIxsoZef9DrY2zKbfvRPqzz5qes%3D%2F501x337%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRPXVLDNMPQAAPGNMYYODOVKW2A.gif&h=cffc324a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8023667d302b199c65c9f74a380c4f594d3f931f","tid":2093618,"uid":28432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:35:06.000Z","msg":"又幾型喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48774f18dcf1b1313d8b20afd3792de934961953","tid":2093618,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"咁撚型"},{"pid":"dedab78f65298423328e4ebd7b0df45c32d254a4","tid":2093618,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8023667d302b199c65c9f74a380c4f594d3f931f","tid":2093618,"uid":28432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T03:35:06